data.description: Experience country living with all the amenities of city life. This wonderfully maintained property is nestled on a three quarter acre lot in Andover. Conveniently located near, schools, parks and shopping. The home offers an open floor plan with a spacious living room, large primary bedroom, two guest-rooms, 2 bathrooms, an open Kitchen/Dining combo and a separate laundry space. Enjoy your morning coffee, quiet sunset or entertain friends and family on the sprawling back deck. If you enjoy home projects, the hobby of wood working, rebuilding cars or just need space to store all your sporting goods and outdoor equipment you're going to love the 35 x 40 Garage. Equipped with 2 12' overhead doors, and one standard 7' side rear overhead door, all with automatic openers and also equipped with 200 amp electrical service. The roof was replaced in 2018 and new HVAC system was installed in 2021 and comes with manufactures warranty. Privacy fence added in 2018, storm doors were also added in 2018, floor jacks were added in the crawl space to maintain level floors and to help prevent creaking. Extensive concrete work and drain tile was added to the driveway to allow for the additional parking to the 35 X 40 outbuilding. Pride of ownership is evident as you pull into the long drive. Schedule your private showing today!
